"Use FileUtil to access configuration":
org.openide.filesystems.Repository.getDefault().getDefaultFileSystem().findResource($p) :: $p instanceof java.lang.String
=>
org.openide.filesystems.FileUtil.getConfigFile($p)
;;

"Use FileUtil to access configuration":
org.openide.filesystems.Repository.getDefault().getDefaultFileSystem().getRoot()
=>
org.openide.filesystems.FileUtil.getConfigRoot()
;;
